name: Manpower Overthrow
description:
A submission for the 8x8 Game Jam 2019; made in Godot Engine.   Source code is included.  This game was created in collaboration with Pobber44.  Never work alone in game development, it is far more enjoyable to do it with others.

Controls:

  • Mouse for clicking on menu buttons & selecting a level.
  • Spacebar spawns an agent.
  • That's it!
